{"id": "art-474", "label": "Art. 474", "title": "Art. 474: Depunerea apelului incident şi a celui provocat", "slug": "art-474", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_694833065\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1237\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_694833065\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 474:\nDepunerea apelului incident &#351;i a celui provocat </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1035782850\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1236\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1035782850\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Apelul incident &#351;i apelul provocat se depun de\nc&#259;tre intimat odat&#259; cu întâmpinarea la apelul principal, fiind\naplicabile prevederile art. 471<sup>1</sup> alin. (4).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1335660803\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1235\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1335660803\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Apelul provocat se comunic&#259; &#351;i intimatului din\nacest apel, prev&#259;zut la art. 473, acesta fiind dator s&#259; depun&#259;\nîntâmpinare în termenul prev&#259;zut la art. 471<sup>1</sup> alin. (4), care\nse aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor. Cel care a exercitat apelul provocat\nva lua cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259; de întâmpinare de la dosarul cauzei.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}